title: Astonishing X-Men by Joss Whedon (Megan-Empire)
description:
Includes:

* Issues #1-24
* Giant-size Astonishing X-Men #1
__
The spiritual successor to Chris Claremont's defining run of the X-Men title and widely regarded as a love letter to Kitty Pryde, this astonishingly sweet title is moving, heartfelt and surprisingly funny. Just as comics are supposed to be...:)

High-quality rips with conservative size, as you see. These ones are keepers!

You may want to use YACReader to open these because it's awesome.
Do consider seeding...:)
